Remember Me 10 of K-Pop's most popular MVs from the '90s By AllK_Maknae 10 minutes ago 4,594 182 0 Intro 10 of K-Pop's most popular MVs from the '90s We love today's groups like EXO, TWICE, BTS and G-Friend because of their trendy, pop songs that are too irresistible to stop listening to. Not only are their songs addicting but their MVs are also just as captivating! However, we can't forget to pay homage to some of the best K-Pop MVs of the '90s that have inspired and paved the way for our favorite artists today. Check out the list of awesome MVs that owned the show during the '90s.
